    "image_prompt": "Editorial tech thumbnail, 16:9. Incorporate the brand logo fetched from https://logo.clearbit.com/flykube.com as the clean focal element over a soft amber-to-cream gradient (Notion + Apple aesthetic). A person with a backpack looking excitedly at a surprise plane ticket or a mystery map of Europe, with iconic landmarks blurred in the background.. Glassmorphism cards, soft volumetric light, generous negative space for a title, no embedded text, no watermark. --ar 16:9 --style raw",
